 so far in 2024, delivering a ~24% total return against the ~10% gain for the broad U.S. real estate ETF:</p> <p>I last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718260-centerspace-increased-2024-outlook-as-occupancy-recovers\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718260-centerspace-increased-2024-outlook-as-occupancy-recovers\" target=\"_blank\">covered the shares back in August</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743881-centerspace-attractively-valued-despite-signs-of-moderating-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 17:53:03"}, {"id": "4743879", "title": "Why Palantir Could Hit $89 Soon", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Grid landscape and glowing particles background\" data-id=\"1196044470\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"7680px\" height=\"4320px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196044470/image_1196044470.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=