\">INTC</a></span>) board arguably had zero reasons to retire Pat Gelsinger as Intel remains on the course it must be on. Of course, its financials aren\u2019t showing this yet, and Intel also hasn\u2019t been successful in some of its newer</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1002010996/image_1002010996.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743867-intel-remains-in-its-investment-phase", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 17:06:35"}, {"id": "4743864", "title": "Visa Inc.: A Strong Buy In The Evolving Financial Landscape", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"VISA Credit Card Wallet\" data-id=\"1319488921\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4032px\" height=\"3024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">FinkAvenue</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Visa Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/V\" title=\"Visa Inc.\">V</a></span>) is one of the most stable stocks in the SP500 index. V, which brings incredibly stable profits both in the short term and the long term, supports this profitability with its innovative and developing structure that perfectly adapts</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1319488921/image_1319488921.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743864-visa-stock-strong-buy-in-evolving-financial-landscape", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 17:04:03"}, {"id": "4743797", "title": "HIVE Digital: I'm Finally A Buyer", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bitcoin sign letter on digital CPU. Crypto concept.\" data-id=\"2186685048\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2186685048/image_2186685048.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/upload